---
title: Beef and Bacon Tacos Norteños with Hot Peppers and Monterey Jack Cheese
description: Norteños are smoky, cheesy tacos from the north of Mexico! In our version, beef and spicy peppers are covered in Monterey Jack and baked until golden, then sprinkled with crispy bacon. An avocado salad is a perfect side to cut through the richness!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tacos-nortenos-au-boeuf-et-au-bacon-f92df1d2.jpg
